OL,3,CPublic invited to scrutinise NHS
OL,4,Cborders at annual review
OL,6,FMembers of the public will have the
OL,7,Fopportunity to scrutinise the future
OL,8,Fdirection of NHS Borders.
OL,10,FThe NHS Borders Annual Review, being
OL,11,Fheld next month, will be a chance to
OL,12,Fhear from board members about their
OL,13,Fchallenges, and how they plan to fix
OL,14,Fit.
OL,16,FIt comes as NHS Borders launched plans
OL,17,Fto slash its budget by more than ten
OL,18,Fper cent.
