OL,6,FThe opening financial position in
OL,7,FApril 2024 had a recurring deficit of
OL,8,F#28 million.
OL,10,FWithout any cost savings being made,
OL,11,Fthis overspend is expected to rise to
OL,12,Faround #40 million at the end of March
OL,13,F2025.
OL,15,FA NHS Borders spokesperson said: "We
OL,16,Fare currently facing unprecedented
OL,17,Fchallenges in planning and delivering
OL,18,Fhealthcare services in the Borders.
