OL,6,F"To address our challenges, we must
OL,7,Finnovate and adapt our approach. This
OL,8,Fmay mean making some difficult
OL,9,Fdecisions about the services we
OL,10,Fprovide.
OL,12,F"The annual review is an opportunity
OL,13,Ffor you to hear and ask questions
OL,14,Fabout the Board's performance in 2023/
OL,15,F24 and our future plans."
OL,17,FThe review will happen on Thursday 22
OL,18,FAugust in the Chaplaincy Centre at
OL,19,FBorders General Hospital in Melrose.
OL,20,FIt runs from 2:30pm to 3:30pm.
