OL,6,FThe session will include a
OL,7,Fpresentation from NHS Borders chair,
OL,8,FKaren Hamilton, followed by an open
OL,9,Fquestion and answer session.
OL,11,FAnyone wishing to attend will need to
OL,12,Fregister their interest by 2 August,
OL,13,Fvia email or my phone on 0800 731 4052.
OL,15,FAnyone wishing to ask questions will
OL,16,Fneed to also submit questions to the
OL,17,Fabove email, by 18 July.
OL,19,FThe meeting will also be available to
OL,20,Fstream online.
